WEBVTT

00:08.520 --> 00:10.150
I'm looking for Mr. Wallace.

00:10.370 --> 00:12.820
He's not here. You got me. Speak.

00:14.130 --> 00:15.710
You knew I was coming, didn't you?

00:15.840 --> 00:16.620
Yeah.

00:17.300 --> 00:18.930
To whine to Mr. Wallace.

00:19.940 --> 00:22.059
This week's check's
60 bucks light, man.

00:22.060 --> 00:23.200
I'm just here to get what's mine.

00:23.480 --> 00:25.309
Question... you think you're pulling

00:25.310 --> 00:26.530
your weight down there, Warner?

00:26.531 --> 00:27.640
What, did my crew say I'm not?

00:27.641 --> 00:28.770
No. I say it.

00:29.290 --> 00:31.650
I see everything you
mokes do and don't do.

00:31.670 --> 00:33.260
That's why you call
me Big Brother, right?

00:33.261 --> 00:35.650
I'm trying to put a down payment
on a ring, man. Come on.

00:35.760 --> 00:38.059
Well, I guess that means
now Connie has time

00:38.060 --> 00:39.520
to find herself a real man.

